    IsIntegralCurveAt Œ≥ v t‚ÇÄ ‚Üî ‚àÉ s ‚àà ùìù t‚ÇÄ, IsIntegralCurveOn Œ≥ v s := by
  simp_rw [IsIntegralCurveOn, ‚Üê Filter.eventually_iff_exists_mem]
